community/debian_6.0/\r\n\r\nif a user logs in using the web interface and uses a different case for their username, and uploads a file, a new folder in the data directory is created along with the file being upload.  when sharing a file link the file will not be found as it is not in the correct folder listed in the database..\r\n\r\na configuration option to force the username and the username in the data folder to be all lower case will prevent this from happening.\r\n\r\ni order to correct this, i had to merge the users folders together to a lowercase folder.  changed the storage directory and username for each user to be lowercase in the database.   run truncate oc_filecache; to rebuild the file cache.  then educate each and every user to only log using a lowercase username.","closed_by":{"login":"vicdeo","id":991300,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/57b8c1e26d502d5414e4b2fb875d2994?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2fe8357fefe8bad5436de368fa5a419461.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"57b8c1e26d502d5414e4b2fb875d2994","url":"https://api.github.com/users/vicdeo","html_url":"https://github.com/vicdeo","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/vicdeo/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/vicdeo/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/vicdeo/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/vicdeo/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/vicdeo/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/vicdeo/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/vicdeo/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/vicdeo/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/vicdeo/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false}}